text: The U.S. Capitol is a surreal place in the midst of a global pandemic. We bring you  into the building with Huddle, the insider’s guide to Congress. Subscribe today for this essential AM read. https://t.co/dfpSNWPYfR https://t.co/MmzN5pxVyb

name: politico
text:
Trump aides are considering shifting the government’s global response to future disease outbreaks to a new unit inside the State Department.

It could establish an alternative mechanism to some of the work done by the World Health Organization.

https://t.co/eBCyIYTI9c
